// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0710 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: fc0389ec-0462-5d4c-b3e4-7cf3425ed2a6

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
